extensive experience in various sectors of the petroleum industry mr montagues nomination was recommended by our general partners board of directors source magellan midstream partners lp on    sign up for equilar atlas and view james r montagues full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like james r montague more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in james r montagues network and community follow changes in james r montagues employment and moneyinmotion connect with james r montague through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example james r montague james r montagues connections  sign up now to view james r montagues  connections » lori a gobillot board member bristow group inc donald f mchenry former board member the cocacola company john t dillon board member kellogg company mark g papa chief executive officer and chairman of the board centennial resource development jeremiah j sheehan former board member universal corporation james p melican former executive vice president international paper company james j postl former board member cooper industries david p obrien former president and chief executive officer elantec semiconductor inc ian w delaney former chairman president and chief executive officer sherritt international corporation michael a grandin former chair and chief executive officer fording canadian coal trust popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla jan koum board member facebook inc philip l milstein board member the marcus corporation × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature is available please enter valid email address done thank you for you